Subject: scsi: smartpqi: Add support for RAID1 writes
Git-commit: 7a012c23c7a7d9cdc7b6db0e8837f8a413dbe436
Patch-mainline: v5.13-rc1
References: bsc#1186472

Add RAID1 write IU and implement RAID1 write support. Change brand names
ADM/ADG to TRIPLE/RAID-6.

